Convert ZX Spectrum screen files to tape files.

12/05/2023 v1.0
    Convert ZX Spectrum screen files to tape files, from the command line.
    scr2tap file1.scr, [file2.scr], [file3.scr] ...

20/05/2023 v1.1
    Added UI.

05/06/2023 v1.2
    New UI.
    Added conversion of screen files to image files in UI.

27/06/2023 v1.3
    UI
        Bin to Tap: Added block type and Address / Line Autoload
        Added Drag an Drop
